the consequences.

1524
01:20:15,898 --> 01:20:17,247
You can't blame
yourself for that.

1525
01:20:17,290 --> 01:20:19,466
This happened
because of me.

1526
01:20:19,510 --> 01:20:21,251
I let that woman
into our house.

1527
01:20:24,210 --> 01:20:25,908
